Constructor Detail

MatchPosition

public MatchPosition(int startLine,
                     int startCol,
                     int endLine,
                     int endCol,
                     int startLineTemplate,
                     int startColTemplate,
                     int endLineTemplate,
                     int endColTemplate,
                     int commentStartCol,
                     int numWords)
Creates a new match position. Column references are to source code files, this is so that the CommentLine is not needed arter the match and so that same MatchPosition can be used both for source files and license files.

Parameters:
startLine - Source file line number where the match starts
startCol - (character) Column where the match starts
endLine - Source file line number where the match ends
endCol - (character) Column where the match ends (inclusive)
startLineTemplate - Template line number where the match starts
startColTemplate - (character) Column where the match starts in template
endLineTemplate - Template line number where the match ends
endColTemplate - (character) Column where the match ends in template (inclusive)
commentStartCol - Column in the file where the comments start (number of characters that have been stripped from the beginning of the line). This is usefull if the file is displayed to the user with only comments.
